{
  "stem": "26983.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to sign something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We are going voluntary to preventive custod-- custod-- preventive prison against the rest of the German people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We go voluntary.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That, we had to sign.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, even that they took our clothes individually and put it in the sack was something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Of course, they didn't give us any receipt for our clothes, but at least they behaved to us in a different way than they usually",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--behaved.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later on, we really came to a kind of sauna.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- we were-- all our hair on, on the-- our hair on the head, they left.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even to the women, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But only the bodily hairs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were shaved.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were put into a terrible Lysol or some solution.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it's not so painful, but bearable.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And afterwards we had to stay for an appell-- waiting.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some water, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were wa-- kind of water.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were waiting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw some installation for disinfection--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were naked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had-- in this winter, we had to wait-- sometimes inside, sometimes outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The very old people, of course, collapsed, and some of them died.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after many hours, we were put in another room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were heaps of clothe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they distributed the clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, of course it didn't fit at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But everyone got something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some piece of-- not a real [YIDDISH], not a real-- how you call it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Something to hold on you your trousers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But elderly people who could still hold their glasses, I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we looked at each other, we couldn't recognize each other, even.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were looking so strange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And for a child it was comic, even, how we looked.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember there was also a heap of gloves.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
